ctrl-a for everything

c or n to create new window
tab or f to go to next window
F to go to previous window
1-9 to go to a specific window that's name is anywhere from 1 to 9
n for new window
h for horizontal split
v for vertical split
r for reload config

Mouse can select pane, window, and text withen pane.
Middle click pastes
Scrolling actually scrolls through history. 
Selecting still works to get things into clipboard.
